{"tid":2188620,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《屍殺半島》登港史上最賣座韓片No.10","createTime":"2020-09-04T10:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T13:46:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"edf6957f2c1e6badfab88ba986de627e81fd6722","tid":2188620,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:55:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200904/KSFSRFHDMVBIBDZTUG7X2UZ4DE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200904%2FKSFSRFHDMVBIBDZTUG7X2UZ4DE%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=f86bec30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200904%2FKSFSRFHDMVBIBDZTUG7X2UZ4DE%2F&h=a17f11f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200904/KSFSRFHDMVBIBDZTUG7X2UZ4DE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n《屍殺半島》登港史上最賣座韓片No.10<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q23pHvm26H4CAChYlbBN2wuwM7c=/960x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HENXRTKM6VA3XBOMDMVWNWL6SY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq23pHvm26H4CAChYlbBN2wuwM7c%3D%2F960x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHENXRTKM6VA3XBOMDMVWNWL6SY.jpg&h=c300f88e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《屍殺半島》男主角姜棟元表示片中的特技是新嘗試。<br />\n<br />\n賣座韓片《屍殺列車》續集《屍殺半島》（半島）上周五在香港戲院解封之日開畫，票房走勢凌厲，首日更狂收224萬，榮登2020年開畫票房No.1。而《半島》在疫情下票房繼續火熱，於電影於上映第6日極速破千萬票房。截至前晚10時，《半島》累積票房成功達1,002萬，更打入香港史上最賣座韓片第10位，第1位為《屍殺列車》，總票房約6,800萬。<br />\n<br />\n《屍殺半島》於香港有多個不同版本選擇，當中比《屍殺列車》用上更多特技，。。。。"},{"pid":"ad815490889661e572015a426ba58eb5ea49282c","tid":2188620,"uid":123020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾片<br />\n悶到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":